RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.CONTRACT_REF_NO, a.user_ref_no, a.product_code, b.product_description, a.counterparty, c.CUSTOMER_NAME1, a.branch, (SELECT facility_name FROM oltbs_contract_master d WHERE d.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no AND version_no = (SELECT MAX(version_no) FROM oltbs_contract_master WHERE contract_ref_no = d.contract_ref_no)) facility_name FROM oltbs_contract a, oltms_product b, oltms_customer c WHERE a.product_code = b.product_code AND a.counterparty = c.CUSTOMER_NO AND a.BRANCH = global.current_branch AND a.module_code IN ('OL') AND a.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'L') ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: sypks_utils.get_branch(CONREFNO) IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVW_USER_BRANCHES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID INTERSECT SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMTB_USER_ROLE WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVWS_USER_CENTRAL_ROLES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT TO_CHAR(NVL(pay_by_date,DUE_DATE),'YYYY-MM-DD') DUE_DATE FROM OLTBS_AMOUNT_DUE WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND (NVL(AMOUNT_DUE, 0) -(NVL(AMOUNT_SETTLED, 0) + NVL(ADJUSTED_AMOUNT, 0))) > 0 ORDER BY DUE_DATE
